From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Sun, 1 Feb 2026 00:39:45 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: cix: Add Sky1 infrastructure drivers

Add pinctrl, GPIO, reset controllers, clock (AUDSS), PWM, watchdog,
hwspinlock, NVMEM, SoC info, DDR low-power, and bus performance drivers
for CIX Sky1 SoC.

Pinctrl uses our generic pinctrl framework implementation with ACPI
support and PM context save/restore, replacing the mainline stub which
uses a different register encoding model.
